{"tid":2391892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"盧寵茂：第三期數據非必要，降落傘是否有三期數據支持？","createTime":"2021-02-02T13:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T13:09:52.000Z","uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2605e6a6ba7b47c935beac5993ff6ff53984754","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"港大深圳醫院院長盧寵茂今日指出，港府預先採購的3款新冠肺炎疫苗存在不確定因素，他認為「寧可備而不用，不可用時無備」，建議港府在等候內地科興疫苗第三期臨床測試報告的同時，應主動出擊，索取國藥集團疫苗的數據交本港專家審批，讓港人能有多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n國藥疫苗已獲國家衛健委批准使用。盧寵茂在電視節目中指出，國藥疫苗屬技術成熟的滅活疫苗，藥廠雖未有在國際醫學期刊上刊登疫苗的第三期臨床數據，但去年已向國家藥監局提交資料，顯示疫苗保護率有79.34%，保護力足夠。他認為港府應主動出擊，更積極地向藥廠索取疫苗資訊。<br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂稱，他身為醫生，同意檢視疫苗第三期臨床數據後才使用是最好的，但在醫學上，決定一種治療或預防方案時，很多時都未必有足夠的第三期數據支持。他又以跳降傘作為比喻，指降傘測試不會有三期數據，「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飛機跳落嚟你要帶降落傘，咁係咪有三期數據支持一定要帶降落傘呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n他認為，如能提供有關數據是理想，但並非必要；本身是肝移植手術專家的他舉例指，肝移植手術也無任何三期數據支持有效。他強調，在疫症大流行中要取得平衡，不能用以前的流程作指標，加上今次的疫苗審批相對較以往嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n他直指，港府已預先採購的3款疫苗都有其不確定因素，如科興未有足夠數據，國家藥監局未審批；復星／BioNTech「復必泰」疫苗可能被限制出口；牛津和阿斯利康疫苗或於今年6月才供貨，所以他呼籲港府主動出擊，積極採購第4款疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502050bf2c8cba8f8c96aedd9291362b0da30e31","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8d5309dd11e97f3812c1c8ff6522b130a332bb","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"咁即係點"},{"pid":"8179afb4a25b38227934a8ea57a6e40b6cec0d93","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d0fe8faa6088fa38e440a3d1a0981e4f2f8c46","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a7ffd7a0777be8350a0d956ee78a7496761b27a3","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"盧醫生"},{"pid":"30aa2db171bdea3150724de8dc3943d1d0ae270a","tid":2391892,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"woohoo"}]}